      "question": "Does the memory item capture the full context necessary to understand the fact without needing the original conversation?",
      "why_it_matters": "Ensures the memory is self-contained and useful for future sessions.",
      "failure_examples": [
        "Storing 'He likes it' without specifying who 'he' is or what 'it' refers to",
