          "rubric_id": "no_hallucination"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "plan_status_presence",
      "name": "Plan and Status Presence",
      "question": "Does the memory set capture plans, intentions, and scheduled items mentioned in the conversation? Are future-oriented statements and their temporal markers preserved?",
      "why_it_matters": "Plans and intentions are memory-worthy content. Missing them loses future-oriented information critical for proactive assistance.",
      "failure_examples": [
        "Conversation states 'Alice will follow up on Monday' but no memory item records this plan",
        "Conversation mentions 'the system upgrade is scheduled for this weekend' but no memory item captures the scheduled upgrade"
      ],
      "source_trace": [
